title: Tantowel - Self-tan towelette how-to application
description:
Exfoliate, tan and moisturize all-in-one with the revolutionary and patented self-tanning towelettes for face and body.

Tantowel towelettes are concentrated with a specialized self-tan formula which works with the proteins and amino acids in skin to produce a healthy and natural sunless tan, unique to you. Full Body towelettes are 9 in. by 12 in. in size for a quick and even application from head to toe with no streaks, mess or fuss. Your sunless tan will develop within 4 hours and last up to 7 days.
